  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"The only allowed skill is counterattack, save the world with PARRY!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your parrying skills in the hardcore action game <i>Parryman</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parrying</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parryman is a game in which you advance using only the counterattack skill of parrying.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parrying is a difficult skill, but can be used to take out most enemies in one hit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some traps can be parried, allowing you to perform a variety of moves with the recoil.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.poster.avif?t=1742542336\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.webm?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.mp4?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A group with powerful science and technology. The island's inhabitants have already succumbed and turned against you, and you must proceed to Parring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras_big/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"The only allowed skill is counterattack, save the world with PARRY!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your parrying skills in the hardcore action game <i>Parryman</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parrying</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parryman is a game in which you advance using only the counterattack skill of parrying.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parrying is a difficult skill, but can be used to take out most enemies in one hit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some traps can be parried, allowing you to perform a variety of moves with the recoil.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.poster.avif?t=1742542336\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.webm?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.mp4?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A group with powerful science and technology. The island's inhabitants have already succumbed and turned against you, and you must proceed to Parring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras_big/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
